OL,3,CInvestigation after passenger train
OL,4,Cderails
OL,6,FAn investigation has been underway
OL,7,Ffollowing the derailment of a
OL,8,Fpassenger train in Darlington.
OL,10,FThe Rail Accident Investigation Branch
OL,11,F(RAIB) said the train "derailed and
OL,12,Fthen rerailed" at Hopetown Junction,
OL,13,Fnear to Darlington North Road station,
OL,14,Fat about 1:19pm on 31 January.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
