OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1772212805
OL,3,CInvestigation after passenger train
OL,4,Cderails
OL,6,FIn a notice published on Tuesday (24
OL,7,FFebruary), the organisation said: "The
OL,8,Ftrain involved had been routed from
OL,9,Fthe Darlington North Road Goods Loop
OL,10,Fline, over the crossover at Hopetown
OL,11,FJunction and onto the Bishop Auckland
OL,12,FSingle line towards Shildon.
OL,14,F"The train crew were initially unaware
OL,15,Fthat anything was amiss and so the
OL,16,Ftrain continued normally to Shildon,
OL,17,Fwhere the driver was alerted to the
OL,18,Fderailment.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1772212805
OL,3,CInvestigation after passenger train
OL,4,Cderails
OL,6,F"A subsequent examination of the train
OL,7,Fand track found evidence that several
OL,8,Fwheels had derailed, and then
OL,9,Frerailed, within the length of the
OL,10,Fcrossover at Hopetown Junction."
OL,12,FThe RAIB confirmed it had carried out
OL,13,Fa preliminary examination and would
OL,14,Fpublish a "safety digest" in the next
OL,15,Ffew weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/3
